statements: SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_id, service_name FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE service_name = 'ServiceA';
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE network_type = 'LAN';
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE configuration ->> 'protocol' = 'TCP';
SELECT service_name, configuration -> 'port' AS port_number FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations ORDER BY service_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations ORDER BY service_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE network_type = 'WAN' AND configuration -> 'firewall' ->> 'status' = 'enabled';
SELECT service_id, network_type FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE configuration -> 'bandwidth' ->> 'unit' = 'Mbps';
SELECT count(*) FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT DISTINCT network_type FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_name, count(*) AS configuration_count FROM NetworkConfigurations GROUP BY service_name;
SELECT service_name, network_type, jsonb_object_keys(configuration) AS config_key FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_name, network_type, jsonb_each_text(configuration) AS config_key_value FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_name, network_type, jsonb_array_elements_text(configuration -> 'interfaces') AS interface FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_name, network_type, jsonb_typeof(configuration) AS config_type FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT service_name, network_type, configuration FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE configuration -> 'firewall' -> 'status' = 'disabled';
SELECT service_name, network_type, configuration FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE configuration @> '{"firewall": {"status": "enabled"}}';
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE service_name LIKE 'Service%' ORDER BY service_id DESC
SELECT service_id, service_name, network_type FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE network_type IN ('LAN', 'WAN')
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE configuration->>'firewall_rule' = 'allow'
SELECT service_id, service_name, count(*) AS config_count FROM NetworkConfigurations GROUP BY service_id, service_name HAVING count(*) > 1
SELECT service_id, service_name, network_type, jsonb_array_elements_text(configuration->'vlans') AS vlan_id FROM NetworkConfigurations
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations JOIN OtherTable ON NetworkConfigurations.service_id = OtherTable.network_service_id
SELECT service_name, jsonb_path_query(configuration, '$.settings[*].gateway') AS gateways FROM NetworkConfigurations
SELECT service_name, jsonb_array_elements_text(configuration->'dns_servers') AS dns_server FROM NetworkConfigurations

SELECT service_id, service_name, network_type FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE network_type = 'LAN' AND JSONB_EXISTS(configuration, 'wifi_settings') AND configuration->'wifi_settings'->>'security' = 'WPA2'

SELECT * FROM service_providers WHERE provider_name LIKE '%abc%';

SELECT * FROM service_providers ORDER BY provider_id DESC;
SELECT AVG(id) FROM network_configurations;
SELECT SUM(id) FROM network_configurations;
SELECT DISTINCT service_name FROM network_configurations;
SELECT * FROM network_configurations WHERE configuration_json ->> 'key' = 'value';
SELECT * FROM service_providers WHERE provider_location IN ('location1', 'location2');
SELECT * FROM network_configurations LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM service_providers OFFSET 5;
SELECT * FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'VPN';
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'host' AS host FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'Web';
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM service_providers;
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'port' AS port FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'Database';
SELECT * FROM network_configurations WHERE configuration_json->'host' = 'example.com';
SELECT DISTINCT service_type FROM network_configurations;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM service_providers WHERE provider_location = 'USA';
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'username' AS username FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'FTP';
SELECT * FROM network_configurations WHERE configuration_json @> '{"ssl": true}';
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM service_providers ORDER BY provider_name DESC;
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'path' AS path FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'File Sharing';
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM network_configurations;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM service_providers WHERE provider_name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'protocol' AS protocol FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'Email';
SELECT * FROM network_configurations WHERE configuration_json ? 'port';
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'ip_address' AS ip_address FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'DNS';
SELECT MAX(id) FROM network_configurations;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM service_providers WHERE provider_location = 'Canada';
SELECT service_name, configuration_json->'password' AS password FROM network_configurations WHERE service_type = 'SSH';
SELECT * FROM network_services;
SELECT service_id, service_name FROM network_services;
SELECT * FROM network_configs;
SELECT config_id, config_name FROM network_configs;
SELECT * FROM network_subscribers;
SELECT subscriber_id, subscriber_name FROM network_subscribers;
SELECT service_name, service_type FROM network_services;
SELECT config_name, config_details FROM network_configs;
SELECT subscriber_name, subscriber_email FROM network_subscribers;
SELECT service_name, service_description FROM network_services;
SELECT config_name, service_id FROM network_configs;
SELECT subscriber_name, service_id FROM network_subscribers;
SELECT * FROM network_services WHERE service_type = 'Type1';
SELECT * FROM network_configs WHERE config_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM network_subscribers WHERE subscriber_name LIKE '%John%';
SELECT service_name, service_type FROM network_services WHERE service_id = 1;
SELECT config_name, config_details FROM network_configs WHERE config_id = 2;
SELECT subscriber_name, subscriber_email FROM network_subscribers WHERE service_id = 3;
SELECT service_name, service_description FROM network_services WHERE service_type = 'Type2';
SELECT config_name, service_id FROM network_configs WHERE config_id = 3;
SELECT subscriber_name, service_id FROM network_subscribers WHERE subscriber_name LIKE '%Smith%';
SELECT * FROM network_services;
SELECT service_id, service_name FROM network_services WHERE service_type = 'VPN';
SELECT * FROM network_configs WHERE service_id IN (SELECT service_id FROM network_services WHERE service_type = 'Firewall');
SELECT * FROM network_configs c JOIN network_services s ON c.service_id = s.service_id;
SELECT s.service_name, c.config_name FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id;
SELECT * FROM network_subscribers WHERE subscriber_email IS NOT NULL;
SELECT s.service_name, sc.subscriber_name FROM network_services s JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id;
SELECT s.service_name, c.config_name, sc.subscriber_name FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id;
SELECT * FROM network_services WHERE service_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10;

SELECT s.service_name, COUNT(sc.subscriber_id) AS subscriber_count FROM network_services s JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name ORDER BY subscriber_count DESC;
SELECT s.service_name, AVG(sc.subscriber_id) AS average_subscribers FROM network_services s JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name;
SELECT s.service_name, MAX(c.config_id) AS max_config_id FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name;
SELECT s.service_name, MIN(c.config_id) AS min_config_id FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name;
SELECT s.service_name, SUM(c.config_id) AS total_config_id FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name;
SELECT s.service_name, AVG(c.config_id) AS avg_config_id FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name HAVING avg_config_id > 5000;

SELECT s.service_name, COUNT(sc.subscriber_id) AS subscriber_count FROM network_services s JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id WHERE subscriber_email IS NOT NULL GROUP BY s.service_name HAVING subscriber_count > 5;
SELECT s.service_name, MIN(c.config_id) AS min_config_id, MAX(c.config_id) AS max_config_id FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id GROUP BY s.service_name;
SELECT s.service_name, jsonb_pretty(c.config_details) AS pretty_config_details FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id;
SELECT DISTINCT s.service_name FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id;
SELECT s.service_name, c.config_name, jsonb_extract_path_text(c.config_details,'version') AS version FROM network_services s JOIN network_configs c ON s.service_id = c.service_id;

SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('service_name', s.service_name, 'subscriber_name', sc.subscriber_name)) AS subscriber_details FROM network_services s JOIN network_subscribers sc ON s.service_id = sc.service_id;
SELECT * FROM NetworkProviders;
SELECT provider_name, service_type FROM NetworkProviders;
SELECT * FROM NetworkDevices;
SELECT device_name, configuration FROM NetworkDevices;
SELECT * FROM NetworkLocations;
SELECT location_name FROM NetworkLocations;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConnections;
SELECT status FROM NetworkConnections;
SELECT provider_name, device_name FROM NetworkProviders JOIN NetworkDevices ON NetworkProviders.id = NetworkDevices.provider_id;

SELECT location_name, device_name FROM NetworkLocations JOIN NetworkConnections ON NetworkLocations.location_id = NetworkConnections.location_id JOIN NetworkDevices ON NetworkConnections.device_id = NetworkDevices.device_id;

SELECT provider_name, location_name, status FROM NetworkProviders JOIN NetworkDevices ON NetworkProviders.id = NetworkDevices.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections ON NetworkDevices.device_id = NetworkConnections.device_id JOIN NetworkLocations ON NetworkConnections.location_id = NetworkLocations.location_id;
SELECT * FROM NetworkProviders;
SELECT provider_name, service_type FROM NetworkProviders WHERE service_type = 'Internet';
SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id;
SELECT nd.device_name, nl.location_name FROM NetworkDevices nd JOIN NetworkLocations nl ON nd.provider_id = nl.location_id;
SELECT np.provider_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id;

SELECT np.provider_name AS Provider, COUNT(nc.status) AS Connection_Count FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id GROUP BY np.provider_name;

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nl.location_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id JOIN NetworkLocations nl ON nc.location_id = nl.location_id;
SELECT DISTINCT np.provider_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id;
SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np LEFT JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id LEFT JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id;

SELECT np.provider_name, SUM(CASE WHEN nc.status = 'Active' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Active_Connections FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id GROUP BY np.provider_name;
SELECT provider_name, COUNT(device_name) AS Device_Count FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id GROUP BY provider_name;
SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id WHERE nd.device_name LIKE '%router%';

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nl.location_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id JOIN NetworkLocations nl ON nc.location_id = nl.location_id WHERE nc.status = 'Active';

SELECT provider_name, MAX(nc.status) AS Max_Status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id GROUP BY provider_name;

SELECT np.provider_name, COUNT(nc.status) AS Connection_Count FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id WHERE nc.status = 'Active' GROUP BY np.provider_name;
SELECT DISTINCT np.provider_name FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id WHERE nd.configuration->>'port' = '22';

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id WHERE nd.configuration @> '{"protocol": "TCP"}';

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id WHERE nd.configuration @> '{"protocol": "HTTP", "port": "80"}' AND nc.status = 'Active';

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id WHERE nd.configuration @> '{"protocol": "TCP"}' AND nd.device_name LIKE '%firewall%';

SELECT np.provider_name, nd.device_name, nc.status FROM NetworkProviders np JOIN NetworkDevices nd ON np.id = nd.provider_id JOIN NetworkConnections nc ON nd.device_id = nc.device_id WHERE nd.configuration @> '{"protocol": "UDP"}' AND nc.status = 'Inactive';
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT id, service_name FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT ip_address, subnet_mask, gateway_address FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE id = 2;
SELECT * FROM ServiceProviders;
SELECT provider_name FROM ServiceProviders WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Subscriptions;
SELECT subscription_type, start_date, end_date FROM Subscriptions WHERE id = 2;
SELECT * FROM Devices;
SELECT device_name, device_type, status FROM Devices WHERE id = 3;
SELECT * FROM Policies;
SELECT policy_name, description FROM Policies WHERE id = 4;

SELECT n.id, n.service_name, s.id AS subscription_id, s.subscription_type, sp.provider_name AS provider_name FROM NetworkConfigurations n JOIN Subscriptions s ON n.id = s.provider_id JOIN ServiceProviders sp ON s.provider_id = sp.id;
SELECT d.device_name, d.device_type, p.policy_name, p.description FROM Devices d JOIN Policies p ON d.provider_id = p.provider_id;
SELECT n.id, n.service_name, d.device_name, d.device_type FROM NetworkConfigurations n JOIN Devices d ON n.id = d.provider_id WHERE d.status = 'active';
SELECT s.provider_id, COUNT(s.id) AS subscription_count FROM Subscriptions s GROUP BY s.provider_id HAVING COUNT(s.id) > 1;
SELECT p.provider_name, COUNT(d.id) AS device_count FROM ServiceProviders p JOIN Devices d ON p.id = d.provider_id GROUP BY p.provider_name ORDER BY device_count DESC;
SELECT n.service_name, AVG(length(s.subscription_type)) AS avg_subscription_length FROM NetworkConfigurations n JOIN Subscriptions s ON n.id = s.provider_id GROUP BY n.service_name;

SELECT p.provider_name, COUNT(d.id) AS device_count, AVG(length(n.service_name)) AS avg_service_name_length FROM ServiceProviders p JOIN Devices d ON p.id = d.provider_id JOIN NetworkConfigurations n ON d.provider_id = n.id GROUP BY p.provider_name;
SELECT DISTINCT(provider_id) FROM Policies;
SELECT DISTINCT(device_name) FROM Devices WHERE status = 'inactive';
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE service_name = 'Internet';
SELECT id, ip_address, subnet_mask FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT Device.device_name, ServiceProviders.provider_name FROM Devices INNER JOIN ServiceProviders ON Devices.provider_id = ServiceProviders.id;
SELECT subscription_type, start_date, end_date FROM Subscriptions WHERE provider_id = 1;
SELECT Policy.policy_name, Policy.description FROM Policies AS Policy WHERE provider_id = 2;
SELECT MAX(id) AS max_id FROM NetworkConfigurations;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total FROM Subscriptions;
SELECT DISTINCT provider_name FROM ServiceProviders;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE gateway_address IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM Devices WHERE status = 'Active';
SELECT * FROM Subscriptions WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';

SELECT Device.device_name, ServiceProvider.provider_name, Subscription.subscription_type FROM Devices AS Device INNER JOIN ServiceProviders AS ServiceProvider ON Device.provider_id = ServiceProvider.id INNER JOIN Subscriptions AS Subscription ON ServiceProvider.id = Subscription.provider_id;

SELECT Device.device_name, Subscription.subscription_type FROM Devices AS Device INNER JOIN Subscriptions AS Subscription ON Device.provider_id = Subscription.provider_id WHERE Device.status = 'Active';
SELECT ServiceProviders.provider_name, COUNT(*) AS total_devices FROM ServiceProviders INNER JOIN Devices ON ServiceProviders.id = Devices.provider_id GROUP BY provider_name;
SELECT ServiceProviders.provider_name, Policies.policy_name FROM ServiceProviders INNER JOIN Policies ON ServiceProviders.id = Policies.provider_id;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE ip_address LIKE '192.%';
SELECT DISTINCT provider_id FROM Devices;
SELECT * FROM NetworkConfigurations WHERE subnet_mask = '255.255.255.0' OR subnet_mask = '255.255.0.0';
SELECT * FROM Devices WHERE provider_id = 3 AND status = 'Inactive';
SELECT Device.device_name, Subscription.subscription_type FROM Devices AS Device LEFT JOIN Subscriptions AS Subscription ON Device.provider_id = Subscription.provider_id;
